      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"StylizedLooks.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/564199461/StylizedLooks.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1755858621658&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=373\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/564199461/StylizedLooks.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1755858621658&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1258\" data-width=\"2557\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"567279619\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"StylizedLooks.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"564199461\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"13\" data-media-id=\"3e391861-bf4a-4a1b-b5db-d76638d8d948\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/564199461/StylizedLooks.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1755858621658&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=746 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/564199461/StylizedLooks.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1755858621658&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=373 1x\"></span><p local-id=\"06ad373881cd\" /><h2 local-id=\"f58af2990923\" id=\"StylizedLooksinSolaris-3StepsForStylizedLooksinHoudiniSolaris\">3 Steps For Stylized Looks in Houdini Solaris</h2><p local-id=\"aae6c11808c4\"><br/>1) Make sure the Stylized Looks AOVs are setup in <strong>RenderMan RenderSettings</strong> node:</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"02.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/564199461/02.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763007498357&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=475\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/564199461/02.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763007498357&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1800\" data-width=\"2880\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"662405225\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"02.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"564199461\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"13\" data-media-id=\"57568aec-4dd1-461b-b955-2be3682846fa\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/564199461/02.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763007498357&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=950 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/564199461/02.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763007498357&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=475 1x\"></span><p local-id=\"529cabc012bf\">2) Insert Stylized Looks Display Filter (ex <strong>PxrStylizedPainterlyBrushXPU</strong>):</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"03.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/564199461/03.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763007544328&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=475\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/564199461/03.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763007544328&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1800\" data-width=\"2880\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"663617604\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"03.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"564199461\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"13\" data-media-id=\"3e1114c2-adf1-4d7e-8fc2-0959072cae61\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/564199461/03.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763007544328&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=950 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/564199461/03.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763007544328&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=475 1x\"></span><p local-id=\"a21f99f4a9b3\">3) Insert <strong>PxrAssign</strong> node to connect Display/Sample filters in scene:</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"04.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/564199461/04.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763007587334&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=475\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/564199461/04.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763007587334&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1800\" data-width=\"2880\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"662995058\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"04.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"564199461\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"13\" data-media